title: No. 19 Georgia loses star RB Nick Chubb to knee injury
text:
> Georgia No. 19 Georgia loses star RB Nick Chubb to knee injury Georgia running back Nick Chubb is helped off the field after injuring his left knee on the first play from scrimmage during an NCAA college football game against Tennessee, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Knoxville, Tenn.
